    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal to ask for someone\u2019s previous salary.",
        "additional_details": "Previous salary should be treated like date of birth or age, gender, disability or trade union membership.",
        "background": "The salary negotiation process, and specifically the gender salary gap is directly affected by a company knowing a person\u2019s previous salary. \r\n\r\nThe salary band for the role should be defined for the role, and based on the responsibility and scope.\r\n\r\nThis shouldn\u2019t be based on the previous salary.",
